                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12861964" author="jdcryans" created="Wed, 28 Apr 2010 22:11:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch adds a new check to .META. (expensive!) before calling setClosing. Also, to lower the .META. stress, it prevents unnecessary puts in postProcessMeta. I&apos;m now able to disable my big table without any issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12861967" author="jdcryans" created="Wed, 28 Apr 2010 22:17:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Testing a bit more with instrumentation, the first part of the patch does nothing. I won&apos;t commit it if this patch is +1ed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12861970" author="stack" created="Wed, 28 Apr 2010 22:24:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 on patch (Reuse the BaseScanner method I&apos;m about to open up with a quit now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12861994" author="jdcryans" created="Wed, 28 Apr 2010 23:25:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch uses &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2497&quot; title=&quot;ProcessServerShutdown throws NullPointerException for offline regions&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-2497&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-2497&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and fixes the condition (and tested that it works like it should).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
